summary: Justin Bieber has been making headlines due to a series of recent events. He paid tribute to his former roommate, Chris King, who was tragically shot dead in Nashville. Despite these personal challenges, Justin has also been showcasing his musical interests, discussing his love for heavy metal bands like Behemoth and Taake. Additionally, Conor McGregor has sent a message to Justin ahead of his upcoming fight, setting a drinking deadline. Justin reportedly declined an offer from Usher to perform at the Super Bowl, further highlighting his current focus and priorities.

summary: Manchester City star Phil Foden is expecting a third child with his girlfriend, Rebecca Cooke. The 23-year-old has been praised by Pep Guardiola for his potential, and the manager believes the arrival of his "third kid" could further enhance his performance. name: Inter Milan
summary: In a thrilling Serie A derby, Inter Milan secured their 20th Italian league title with a 2-1 victory over city rivals AC Milan. Francesco Acerbi and Marcus Thuram scored the crucial goals for Inter, while Milan's Olivier Giroud scored a consolation. The match was marred by three red cards and multiple scuffles in stoppage time, reflecting the intense rivalry and high stakes of the fixture. Inter's triumph marks a historic moment for the club, as they now sit alongside Juventus as the most successful teams in Serie A history. The victory also gives Inter manager Simone Inzaghi his first league title in his second season in charge, while rival Milan manager Stefano Pioli falls just short of his first title at the San Siro.
